"Jaded (These Years)"

There's a time and place, for everything.

There's a destination, for everyone.
What's the explanation, when we're done?

All the summer nights spent wondering;
So many questions asked, but no one's answering.
Would it be okay if I left today?
Took my chances on what you said was wrong?

I'm jaded, stupid, and wreckless.
Not sorry, and I'll never regret.
These years spent, so faded and wreckless.
Not sorry, and I'll never regret these years.
I'll never regret these years.

Now here i sit, so far away.
Remembering all our memories.

Not sorry, we'll never regret.

We'll never forget the places we've been, you and i.

Don't want to let time pass us by, byyyyyyy...

These years....
...spent, so faded and wreckless,

Not sorry, and I'll never regret these years.

ANYWAYS

<FONT color=#000000><FONT size=4>         I now understand the pain people feel for those in iraq. I came home today and my dad said, "sit down ive got something to tell you." and i knew it wasnt going to be good. i was like whats wrong. and he says, "micheal ( my next door neighbor) had been in iraq for about 2 months now and was riding with his sargent to camp in a hum-v and the hum-v was blown up." my heart stop. i swear i think i actually felt it stop for a second. all i could think of was the worst. he had been killed and now his 3 month old daughter and new wife had to face the fact he wasnt coming home. i started to tear up. and he said there is good new too. and i had hope. he said, "he wasnt killed but is very badly injured. he lost most of his hearing and shatered several disks in his back. he is in the hospital and doing ok but still will never be the same micheal he was when he left. the sargent he was riding with is dying fast and wont hold on much longer. all i want right now is for him to come back home. so to all you out there that have some one in iraq ... i say just hold on and prey every night that they return home safely. whether they arnt the same person when they left or not ... atleast there home. stay brave and never loose hope. i prey for all those solders that had to go to iraq, may God be with you and you return home soon!</FONT> </FONT>

this weekend started off good and ended even better! friday i hung out with kyle. i swear all we did was hang out. we watched whos line is it anyways. its one of my favorite tv shows. haha. anyways i had to be home at 11:30 which really sucked but its ok cuase i was really tired anyways. 
    PROM DAY!
  when i woke up on sat. i called kim and she came over so we could go get a few things done before prom. she talked me into that spray tan shit... DONT EVER TRY. it turned out orangy but i have to admit it didnt look that bad. it was only orange in certain lights. its faded alot but still there so its not as orange anymore. yahhhh. anyways i went to go get my hair done and it turned out REALLY good. i loved it. simple yet awesome. it wasnt curled but she had flipped and pinned my hair to where it looked like it was, then i had twirled hair around that. it was pretty or atleast i though so. lol. after i got that done i went over to kims to get ready we were ready soooo early ... or so we thought. when becca called i realized my toe nails and make up hadnt been touched yet. so we missed pictures. finally the boys showed up. they looked soooooooooo good. oh my word. we got to dinner and i had sooo much fun. i dont think ive laughed that hard in a while. anyways i had alot of fun at prom unfortunately. i mean its not exactly a bad thing but i was doing so well not having crushes. and it really dont help that ive already tried and things went really bad last time we tried dating. but theres something about that boy that just wont let me go. no matter how hard i try i end up kissin i him at the end of the night knowing it dont mean anything to him. or so i think. i know how he is tho and no matter how much i fall for him i know i cant have him .. not becuase he dont like me (even tho he dont) but becuase i dont want to start something if i know from the beginning it will end bad. you know. so to answer a bunch of yalls question do i like him ... my answer is ... no, yes, no, idk, I CANT! after prom we went to franks house to change then we to drews friends house for like 2 sec. and left becuase it was ssooooooooooooo gay. then we just went to kims house and slept. what a night. i just wished i partied more. haha. i wanted to get piss as drunk. i went home with only a buzz. i was pissed. but yah prom was really fun and i dont regret anything i just wished it meant something to him not just me. :(

finally its friday. toke long enough. i miss spring break sooo much. i had sooo much fun wilin out with kimbo, tommy, burto, brandon, chris and robby. wow thats sounds slutty ... there were girls there i just didnt really know them. prom is tomorrow and im soooo stoked. haha. i still have to order the bootenear and maybe find different shoes but its all good. i think i might be going with daniel and becca to dinner now since no one else will help me figure it out. kim is but brandon and frank DEFF arnt! lmao. afterward i think were going to party with cassie and the rest of them so you know well be wasted. lol. its all good. thrusday at school we had an assembly about drinking and driving and they showed like actual wrecked cars that had been in fatal crashes. the had them set up like they had hit and had the drama kids act like it was them that had just got hit. kelly cassidy actually got into the body bag! oh was she brave. haha. tonight im hanging out with kyle .... odd huh? thats what i thought. but i really am trying to be his friend again. ive been a big bitch lately ... sorry to everyone. i really didnt realize it till robby said something to me. my bizzle. lol haha right robby! well i got to go get ready for tonight. bye bye boo!

hey boo! lol! today was just another day ... kinda! i had orientation for work today. it turns out i do work with that voodoo girl. lol! this is her second job so i guess she dropped out of school. what a surprise right. lol sorry that was mean. i talked to kyle today for the first time in like 2 months. we only talked for like 5 minutes cuase he was going to a practice with john of some sort idk. but its cool he said he would call me when hes done .. lets see how true to his word he can be! lol! probably not very .. but idk we'll see. im starting to like this single thing. cause i can flirt all i want and cant get into trouble. or just have fun with some guy friends with out a b/f to get in the way and be jealous that i have guy friends that arnt his friends too. lol! relationships are alot of drama. so im good for now. ive got another date this weekend :) me and justin leg. are suppose to go out. i hope we actually do. i know i say i like being single but i want someone to hold me too! you know? lol! confusing i know! but im going to go get ready for bed! goodnight boo! haha!

ANOTHER BIG SURPRISE! lol! i thought he didnt even want have anything to do with me for awhile. but .. i dunno. then we went over to chris's house and hung out with the group. i had fun but i feel asleep and they told me i woke up yelling at the for fighting ... i guess they had gotten into a fight or something ... i do remember hearing the f word alot tho. lol.

SUNDAY~ i start work tomorrow and im nervous. i was told im doing orientation with this girl name rosie. i went to elementary with her and shes a freak.. and i dont mean gothic .. well she is but shes into the whole voodoo and witchcraft shit. and shes just not someone i want to be around. lol! i hope im not tho. but i think im going to go wash my car now. peace out cou!

which really turns out to be good for me! .... with me stressin out and all that hes dealing with we dont need the drama of a relationship on top of that! so im not complaining... ryan if your reading this and i misunderstood anything you told me last night ... tell me! lol! but i have like 3 projects to do plus some algebra homework so im going to go do that shit! lol! peace out cou!
